data.text: @Peter_F_Ryan @abcnews Totally agree. So professional. I was travelling in Russia and now Austria and followed everything. I am very tired ...

@Peter_F_Ryan @abcnews I call 'bullshit' on this, Peter. It was NOT "a big day in Australian history".
Metaphorically, a tablecloth on a very wonky table was changed, the table is still what it is. Nothing of any substance has actually changed, nor will it change as a result of changing the tablecloth.

@Peter_F_Ryan @LisaMillar @abcnews Thank you @Peter_F_Ryan, may we ask what do #Australians want of their #leaders?
What did you learn from the #leadership of @TurnbullMalcolm?
@Peter_F_Ryan @abcnews Imagine if you went camping out bush last Saturday and only came back to phone and radio coverage today - you’d get quite a shock!
